Name: SMF30_US_ComprReq
Description: Total number of compression and decompression requests (both supervisor-state and problem-state requests)

Name: SMF30_US_ComprReq_Prob
Description: Total number of problem-state compression and decompression requests.

Name: SMF30_US_QueueTime
Description: Total queue time. The amount of time, in microseconds, from when the request was submitted until the adapter started executing the request.

Name: SMF30_US_Def_UncomprIn
Description: Total number, in bytes, of uncompressed data input.

Name: SMF30_US_Def_ComprOut
Description: Total number, in bytes, of compressed data output.

Name: SMF30_US_Inf_ComprIn
Description: Total number, in bytes, of compressed data input.

Name: SMF30_US_Inf_DecomprOut
Description: Total number, in bytes, of decompressed data output.
